I. Principal Architectures & Methodologies
This project incorporates original architectures and methodologies developed by Eunkyum Kim. Key technical pillars include:

* Hybrid ESKF-Stateful TCN: A closed-loop architecture integrating Error-State Kalman Filters with Temporal Convolutional Networks.
* Non-linear Reverse Engineering of Hovering: A methodology for reconstructing physical depth from normalized 2D digitizer signals.
* O(1) Stateful Inference: Optimized real-time inference using ring buffers for resource-constrained edge devices.


